issue_place_s: Burlington, New Jersey, United States of America
issue_obverse_legend_s: FIFTEEN SHILLINGS. | THIS BILL is by an ORDINANCE of the Provincial Congress, shall pass current in all Payments within the Colony of New-Jersey, for FIFTEEN SHILLINGS, Proclamation Money. Dated the 20th Day of February 1776. | FIFTEEN Shillings.
issue_reverse_legend_s: Fifteen Shillings. | BURLINGTON, | in New-Jersey, | Printed by Isaac Collins, 1776.
